<sect1 id="dir_b2dc284bc44df997cbbb992175867665_1autotoc_md176">
<title>HealthComponent</title><para>Manages health state for an entity:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput>takeDamage(float)</computeroutput> - Reduces health (clamped to 0)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>heal(float)</computeroutput> - Increases health (clamped to max)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>isAlive()</computeroutput> - Returns true if health &gt; 0</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>reset()</computeroutput> - Restores health to maximum</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>Health is automatically reset when the component is acquired from a pool.</para>
